body_html:
The following DLLs are typically part of a CUDA Toolkit installation:

  • CUBLAS64_80.DLL
  • CUFFT64_80.DLL
  • CURAND64_80.DLL
  • CUSOLVER64_80.DLL

Perhaps you need to reinstall CUDA 8.0 to get these DLLs? (I believe the other three are false negatives.)

body:
The following DLLs are typically part of a CUDA Toolkit installation:

* `CUBLAS64_80.DLL`
* `CUFFT64_80.DLL`
* `CURAND64_80.DLL`
* `CUSOLVER64_80.DLL`

Perhaps you need to reinstall CUDA 8.0 to get these DLLs? (I believe the other three are false negatives.)
